## 🧠 NLP Concepts Used

- **LSA (Latent Semantic Analysis)** — Identifies most important sentences mathematically
- **POS Tagging** — Detects proper nouns for owner identification
- **Regex Pattern Matching** — 28 action patterns and 10 date patterns
- **Keyword Classification** — Auto-assigns High, Medium, Low priority
- **Named Entity Detection** — Finds responsible person from email content


## ⚠️ Note on Dataset

The Enron dataset file `emails.csv` is not included in this repository due to its large size (500MB+). Please download it from Kaggle and place it in the `data/` folder before running the project.

👉 https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/wcukierski/enron-email-dataset

